data.description: Calling all investors or entrepreneurs looking to start your own business !! This is a perfect buy and hold opportunity or a great location to start your own business and live on the second floor. First floor commercial space is huge and is perfect for so many types of businesses. Above the commercial space is a massive 2 bedroom / 1 bath apartment space that has the same footprint as the first floor. The property has a great basement space with high ceilings that can be finished off or used as storage. Septic and well are 3 years old, first floor has a 2 year old tankless water heater, and the second floor water heater is about 10 years old. Do not pass up this one of a kind investment. Second floor is currently occupied on a month-to-month lease but tenant is willing to sign a new lease so you’d only need to rent out the commercial space. Buyer to pay for sellers closing costs. Property is sold in AS-IS condition. Inspections are for informational purposes only. Buyer responsible for all requirements to occupy as needed by the township. Cash only.
